headline: EQT Corporation Secures 20-Year LNG Export Agreement with Commonwealth LNG
summary: EQT Corporation (NYSE:EQT) is one of the best inexpensive stocks to buy according to hedge funds. On September 8, EQT Corporation announced a 20-year Sale and Purchase Agreement/SPA with Commonwealth LNG. Under this agreement, EQT has secured 1 million tonnes per annum/MTPA of liquefaction capacity at Commonwealth LNG’s export facility, which is currently under development […]
